Subject: Upgrade to NEA (NAA) v11.6.0.138
Description:
To address a bug in our sharepoint SDD scans, we need to upgrade several components to the latest CU release (11.6.0.138).  We are currently at 11.6.0.134.

The following components need to be updated:

 - proxy agents and SDD plugins
 - NEA and SDD module
 - AIC

Best,
Todd Wyman
What_We_Know__c: The customer was advised to upgrade to the latest version of the NEA to address a bug in SharePoint SDD Scan.
Solution_Comment__c: I upgraded the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor and the Access Information Center to the latest version.
